In this work, the isotope amount content and activity measurements are used to derive a value for the 243Am half-life. A comparison is made with previously published measurement results [23–31] and evaluated values by the Decay Data Evaluation Project (DDEP) and Nuclear Data Sheets (NDS) [13, 32]. Figure 1 shows a schematic overview of the techniques used and the observables obtained through a relative and absolute method, as explained futher on in the paper. All uncertainty values in this work pertain to the standard uncertainty.Fig. 1
